{"tid":284690,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急求救]屋企條大魚沉底扮比目魚 點算？","createTime":"2017-06-15T06:53:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T08:28:54.000Z","uid":113873,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"94fc13d73638517d7b96c7533fd56218c0508842","tid":284690,"uid":113873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T06:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/144918_e883e77e6a14d567aee8af2768078ccd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F144918_e883e77e6a14d567aee8af2768078ccd.jpg&h=d569e2cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點算呀？我可以點做？條魚老豆養咗十年多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一直都好健康，今朝一起身就沉咗底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba990940c699917514b884b2f617bd24400b224c","tid":284690,"uid":40272,"like":53,"dislike":3,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T06:54:53.000Z","msg":"今晚加餸"},{"pid":"f6832ea095dfe0462f0beaf0fabb3df0e55ff929","tid":284690,"uid":90690,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T06:55:01.000Z","msg":"咩魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c98f4a28874f56d1bf2eb2bc3ce9d5e0b36ffd9","tid":284690,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T06:55:09.000Z","msg":"乜魚黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e05a3d1bdbc63e0b87d0aca46f4af308369cba3a","tid":284690,"uid":81389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T06:56:21.000Z","msg":"換完水？"},{"pid":"a9944c7bb37df0c03102a761434a18c2cbd912b0","tid":284690,"uid":113873,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T06:57:04.000Z","msg":"連濾水器都一齊壞咗<br />\n於是我用花灑拎高咁加水落去，希望打啲氧氣落去，依家佢個樣好咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4092bdb28b2fdc5bb98078e3bed0e08cc11e5a","tid":284690,"uid":113873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T06:57:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>換完水？</blockquote><br />\n無呀，應該關唔夠氧事"},{"pid":"3935c1073c3a8af55df48365cb5876b881ed8a3f","tid":284690,"uid":113873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T06:58:35.000Z","msg":"正經post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f085844e98e745e86f3cc1a60c70f58c284b4218","tid":284690,"uid":113873,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/145925_34ff0826b826d6e1187df1c2e2a31d41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F145925_34ff0826b826d6e1187df1c2e2a31d41.jpg&h=33f9f1e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢不停浮上去抖氣"},{"pid":"4bf5804e6901745f90db7944339b1a87b32dcc3d","tid":284690,"uid":64133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:01:06.000Z","msg":"魚要瞓覺㗎"},{"pid":"0af25335756088b3edb0d77f47e8816609d476f7","tid":284690,"uid":113873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:01:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>魚要瞓覺㗎</blockquote><br />\n日頭呀！佢瞓醒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d3679e603cf1fb9b8500f3d99401a7ea74962b","tid":284690,"uid":26084,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:01:46.000Z","msg":"明知係set 嘢壞就快D去換啦屌"},{"pid":"570961b7a284a5922d522b8efd4930539b8a2831","tid":284690,"uid":74146,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:03:25.000Z","msg":"煎定炸好"},{"pid":"e22fbcbb41c15f251e840847a3538f40de4aed90","tid":284690,"uid":113873,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:04:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明知係set 嘢壞就快D去換啦屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔識買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條魚係我屋企人養<br />\n我search多陣就出街買啦"},{"pid":"86614055ed9987e7a774b151e9c956499b2ef3f7","tid":284690,"uid":74598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:04:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>煎定炸好</blockquote><br />\n清蒸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1dd9ec20ea203db36cd02c6b4abf496d0e62085","tid":284690,"uid":111628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:04:59.000Z","msg":"RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ec2d5429aec2dfaca88498335b3968bc962896","tid":284690,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be46c70345f5ca719604daad4cbe0e808721176","tid":284690,"uid":68028,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:05:31.000Z","msg":"咩魚黎 咁醜樣嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf83ac8bec3bfd4cfc338f3ca465fd598463a9cd","tid":284690,"uid":113873,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:09:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩魚黎 咁醜樣嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n招財魚好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/150909_fd36f30f5884680ec4102a9936d0b94c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F150909_fd36f30f5884680ec4102a9936d0b94c.jpg&h=70a29163&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22572adbaf3b87e1f36147308690495596dc48c8","tid":284690,"uid":113873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:10:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5880934c8c6eeb0d8f582a93c3679deb3871f7de","tid":284690,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:10:48.000Z","msg":"你老豆呢？"},{"pid":"d412e8d5b2b20c041fd4350dbef270b70868f8cb","tid":284690,"uid":113873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:12:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老豆呢？</blockquote><br />\n返緊工"},{"pid":"6f872cd56a2698fc6281fbd900363fb5b5593225","tid":284690,"uid":81389,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:12:41.000Z","msg":"佢係戰船魚/絲足魚，係屬迷鰓類。同萬隆、珍珠馬甲果D一樣會上水呼吸。"},{"pid":"0700b544c2c7412800642833a7d1e5717d341b4d","tid":284690,"uid":113873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:13:47.000Z","msg":"氣泵應該點樣揀？係咪度完個魚缸size再去水族店問就ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e94bdd69487cd2d8557145c3084709ab97722f22","tid":284690,"uid":113873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:15:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢係戰船魚/絲足魚，係屬迷鰓類。同萬隆、珍珠馬甲果D一樣會上水呼吸。</blockquote><br />\n佢係沉咗底好耐唔郁，係我加咗水佢先活潑少少 識得浮上去呼吸<br />\nAnyway唔該哂巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e04bc852bf5f019649c37a4ad92c88de7a838d1","tid":284690,"uid":81389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:17:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>氣泵應該點樣揀？係咪度完個魚缸size再去水族店問就ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你度左個缸幾大，平時水位幾高去問喇。影埋壞左果個濾水器比魚店的人睇，因為濾水器都有好多種。你影埋比佢地睇最穩陣。"},{"pid":"88b53da9770ed7488d3c14ecaa8945ed47699ade","tid":284690,"uid":90820,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:17:28.000Z","msg":"咁一係樓主托住佢<br />\n等佢keep住係水面換到氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac9f6b92f5f883cdefe642f7911342ab265a28f","tid":284690,"uid":45684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:18:27.000Z","msg":"問你老豆要買咩, 去邊間舖買"},{"pid":"698274d47ffaf0de0b1554a420271edf721633b5","tid":284690,"uid":6752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:18:32.000Z","msg":"拆左佢比鋪頭睇最簡單架啦,反正都係壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4f0d2e87225815e19897bb5a1040ef021804a0","tid":284690,"uid":37343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:18:45.000Z","msg":"小心唔好亂加太多生水，否則好快瓜"},{"pid":"0875f4c17edb186810fee91105d49d5e93c4c319","tid":284690,"uid":26084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:18:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>明知係set 嘢壞就快D去換啦屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔識買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條魚係我屋企人養<br />\n我search多陣就出街買啦</blockquote><br />\n影相，落金魚街買返一樣"},{"pid":"6a27c1ca3b504b88e3eebdbc4698ed7578d8175f","tid":284690,"uid":113873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:21:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小心唔好亂加太多生水，否則好快瓜</blockquote><br />\n知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我留咗一桶水曬緊太陽，但唔知咁短時間內有冇用？"},{"pid":"506e2942906f9fc8683aad5e53c9f8a6fc911d04","tid":284690,"uid":113873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:33:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca4e72e7a70f4aa173efd9e9d19757bfc5384e54","tid":284690,"uid":34368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:39:40.000Z","msg":"買個氣泵打大氣"},{"pid":"65c4080ecd404afe5f5a57bb4fa57488a1c9039b","tid":284690,"uid":15622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:42:36.000Z","msg":"插支飲管落去吹氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3260741c0b733568cd5330762e244b46ca2e2fa2","tid":284690,"uid":35520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:45:39.000Z","msg":"拎飲管吹氣比佢頂住先"},{"pid":"853a808aa6f20c688e15ed4099600ded1ed2bf09","tid":284690,"uid":22803,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:47:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>插支飲管落去吹氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個啊爸都係咁對我條金魚仔 2個鐘之就死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d934735b10dfe637306768653d27c1939e1155e","tid":284690,"uid":34955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:51:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小心唔好亂加太多生水，否則好快瓜</blockquote><br />\n知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我留咗一桶水曬緊太陽，但唔知咁短時間內有冇用？</blockquote><br />\n記得唔好餵野食<br />\n筆起啲舊水再倒返落去已經打到唔小氣<br />\n唔好用新水<br />\n<br />\n依家狗衝去買個打氣先<br />\n再留一桶水買完野返緊換水用<br />\n記得所有野都係洗乾淨至好用"},{"pid":"c803e95e7cf8a68f929efca6e0e8b993bc1b2cfb","tid":284690,"uid":91730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:52:37.000Z","msg":"濾水器同氣泵一齊壞？<br />\n其實你有冇諗過係電既問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2da449c8bd16e5c596c28ce0a3c78558132e50b","tid":284690,"uid":113873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:00:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>濾水器同氣泵一齊壞？<br />\n其實你有冇諗過係電既問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係電問題啦 我試過插其他電器<br />\n我老豆用果款係氣泵濾水器連埋"},{"pid":"70987e210c7f48dcc778750c4e1f2a1a1c335f29","tid":284690,"uid":96218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:00:25.000Z","msg":"少年水族師召喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e57786e40237ff9a1f0aac09512d6f2202db5f9","tid":284690,"uid":3032,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:04:44.000Z","msg":"屌    直接加水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n水喉水有6氣   要放幾日先好養魚<br />\n成日上水抖氣姐係水唔夠氧<br />\n快手好買氣bump啦"},{"pid":"f3c7411975b836a1603a2b8f2a034abda8f26cce","tid":284690,"uid":4531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:05:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"76f803fb0273b7f8450a44290980aa75114ed3fc","tid":284690,"uid":111522,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:10:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>氣泵應該點樣揀？係咪度完個魚缸size再去水族店問就ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n是但買個氣泵先啦，難道你呼吸困難，D救護員同連登仔講，要囗罩是否要度身訂造口罩先，然後幾個鐘頭後先比氧氣你呀"},{"pid":"3c4b46462fd036e65230fdbf67bcdde63372624c","tid":284690,"uid":4392,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:24:08.000Z","msg":"用飲管吹其實係咪會吹番呼出黎d 二氧化碳落去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"884bc0ff95d479ee47c52ab6bc0013a51381f94a","tid":284690,"uid":92704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:28:36.000Z","msg":"Call白車"},{"pid":"a8b1813163abac6939f38d0fe07aecf96a2233be","tid":284690,"uid":69417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:29:46.000Z","msg":"買過條扮無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3a433944b1958dba758a96ff7bfb910012de80","tid":284690,"uid":11698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:30:40.000Z","msg":"同我立即去買電芯氣泵兩個打大氣。<br />\n<br />\n水開定1/4缸既水量 放一晚除氯氣 聽朝換水。<br />\n<br />\n然後都未死就換左個過濾器去。"},{"pid":"5ee26f38c61e1db26d1d7e8cf85093448bc9f91c","tid":284690,"uid":78829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:33:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>