"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n是但買個氣泵先啦，難道你呼吸困難，D救護員同連登仔講，要囗罩是否要度身訂造口罩先，然後幾個鐘頭後先比氧氣你呀</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a266a8f4d96ff5f1b12e9e2103f79e523ef4f5c4","tid":284690,"uid":68491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T12:39:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>氣泵應該點樣揀？係咪度完個魚缸size再去水族店問就ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n是但買個氣泵先啦，難道你呼吸困難，D救護員同連登仔講，要囗罩是否要度身訂造口罩先，然後幾個鐘頭後先比氧氣你呀</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老實講一條魚 是但一個氣泵都夠"},{"pid":"fc66aec77d89a5b7eb5be31ec7ba9db5fe81e3cd","tid":284690,"uid":743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T12:42:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用飲管吹其實係咪會吹番呼出黎d 二氧化碳落去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁人供呼吸咪姐係謀殺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71b1346cd62ac9abfac279f0d7048fd9bc57561","tid":284690,"uid":5026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:19:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用飲管吹其實係咪會吹番呼出黎d 二氧化碳落去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你呼出嚟個d都唔係純co2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登真係好多弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n究竟連登係真係咁多小學雞定係少少常識都無</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係痴撚線</blockquote><br />\n你識條毛，人地呼吸系統效能高，吸一啖就可以換晒d 氧做co2, 之後可以閉氣幾粒鐘</blockquote><br />\n嘩 咁對住人不斷吹氣就可以完美殺人"},{"pid":"ace4540f8e80bcba19ec1c257a80ac0fa78a439c","tid":284690,"uid":109703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:24:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條魚咁柒 掉左佢算數啦</blockquote><br />\n咁你都掉左自己啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3071c1cd0c924848c7ab28501ffe6714f2e29b9","tid":284690,"uid":30487,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:31:09.000Z","msg":"我諗只係因為壞左過濾令水質變差同埋含氧量低<br />\n買返個上水泵換落去就得<br />\n個水泵有寫牌子型號流量<br />\n影張相去跟住買返就得<br />\n買嗰陣唔需要同店員有任何交流<br />\n一手交錢一手交貨<br />\n當你一問<br />\n佢地就知道你唔識<br />\n會水你買啲唔需要嘅野<br />\n你當自己係水族師咁行入去行返出黎就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後換7成水<br />\n加水慢慢加<br />\n白綿污糟就換<br />\n得閒就洗埋濾材<br />\n沖沖水就得<br />\n咁基本上都無乜問題<br />\n呢啲魚粗生到爆<br />\n原本係食用魚黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n長遠黎講加個氣泵好啲<br />\n雖然唔加都得<br />\n但有總好過冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以去金魚街卡奇買勁靜G30<br />\n$150左右，最抵用<br />\n夠勁夠靜夠平夠耐用<br />\n<br />\n上面好多話咩新水唔可以即刻落缸<br />\n又話咩自來水有氯氣<br />\n其實唔撚驚<br />\n驚就買支去氯劑就得<br />\n而正路黎講<br />\n如果唔係住村屋/唐樓/大廈低層或者個別會自己再加氯嘅屋苑<br />\n基本上自來水直車入缸都無問題<br />\n我就是成功的例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多人都未試過就聽人講唔可以咁做<br />\n怯你就輸一世！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放膽試一次就明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">衰左嘅話最多都係死魚姐無咩野</span>"},{"pid":"25db8afa6a518aaa9770d46e08971c802376b4a4","tid":284690,"uid":56699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:31:47.000Z","msg":"而家點？"},{"pid":"6fdf374382e6ea0a4aea6151dd77d18264f14c14","tid":284690,"uid":81575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:37:25.000Z","msg":"是撚但買個最平既頂住先<br />\n等老豆俾來先買個長用架啦"},{"pid":"7d5a7c21d4e5e2691a48a6d34dcde0628342a50e","tid":284690,"uid":76148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T14:20:20.000Z","msg":"海底奇兵"},{"pid":"ec8c1b08382b60e67f5b65ef5df0c95ca521fb87","tid":284690,"uid":51436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:01:05.000Z","msg":"花羅漢？"},{"pid":"6037668b4fcae6d365101591feed0e8797b0a4af","tid":284690,"uid":65234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:12:14.000Z","msg":"面青口唇白喎佢"},{"pid":"15283856539ab512186f7a9558b104876d426157","tid":284690,"uid":104748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:31:47.000Z","msg":"樓主呢？俾條魚食咗？"},{"pid":"50f9110df8e699c2d554d56342d69dcf918288e0","tid":284690,"uid":108422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:42:18.000Z","msg":"樓主做緊海底奇兵？條魚而家點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eeb860c8f3f7b1a635bde70eaace8fc7e6909e1","tid":284690,"uid":113873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:50:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗只係因為壞左過濾令水質變差同埋含氧量低<br />\n買返個上水泵換落去就得<br />\n個水泵有寫牌子型號流量<br />\n影張相去跟住買返就得<br />\n買嗰陣唔需要同店員有任何交流<br />\n一手交錢一手交貨<br />\n當你一問<br />\n佢地就知道你唔識<br />\n會水你買啲唔需要嘅野<br />\n你當自己係水族師咁行入去行返出黎就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後換7成水<br />\n加水慢慢加<br />\n白綿污糟就換<br />\n得閒就洗埋濾材<br />\n沖沖水就得<br />\n咁基本上都無乜問題<br />\n呢啲魚粗生到爆<br />\n原本係食用魚黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n長遠黎講加個氣泵好啲<br />\n雖然唔加都得<br />\n但有總好過冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以去金魚街卡奇買勁靜G30<br />\n$150左右，最抵用<br />\n夠勁夠靜夠平夠耐用<br />\n<br />\n上面好多話咩新水唔可以即刻落缸<br />\n又話咩自來水有氯氣<br />\n其實唔撚驚<br />\n驚就買支去氯劑就得<br />\n而正路黎講<br />\n如果唔係住村屋/唐樓/大廈低層或者個別會自己再加氯嘅屋苑<br />\n基本上自來水直車入缸都無問題<br />\n我就是成功的例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多人都未試過就聽人講唔可以咁做<br />\n怯你就輸一世！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放膽試一次就明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">衰左嘅話最多都係死魚姐無咩野</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n水族師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條魚真係好粗養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我老豆換水都係直接水喉水加 又成日餵生果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢種魚養咗好多年，係得呢條有食生果，結果最長命係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f001e292e864865daaca4967c768778277b0054c","tid":284690,"uid":113873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:51:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>面青口唇白喎佢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好青"},{"pid":"e3a991d4274b351ac516ce9f857855b8b5710f5b","tid":284690,"uid":113873,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T16:08:33.000Z","msg":"各位唔好意思，上黎報告返情況先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條魚醒返啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢平時見到手指會追住黎咬，依家比手指佢都冇乜反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望唔好因為缺氧變咗傻魚啦<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/16/000253_3981bf2a844ccf197212e1beb04f30a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2F000253_3981bf2a844ccf197212e1beb04f30a6.jpg&h=2d9bd297&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢個樣真係似隔離post個巴打咁講有啲得戚既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇完他媽歌詞巴打既建議，我用舊水整啲水流，結果都唔錯<br />\n後尾老豆趕返屋企搞下個氣泵，原來係濾水器塞咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到氧氣泵都停埋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝哂咁多位巴絲認真詳細幽默既解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw今晚冇大魚食，不過老母真係煎咗比目魚食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/16/000812_2e9fdad5d4d55584eec08e45cc3195a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2F000812_2e9fdad5d4d55584eec08e45cc3195a2.jpg&h=7a8fa36d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食到好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99fcc80450605f292f70e3103a1a3c54b615873","tid":284690,"uid":33756,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T16:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你係咪女人？ 咁撚蠢都有嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0778f62251b92ee77b195d2b0b6218c500fec215","tid":284690,"uid":113873,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T16:25:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你係咪女人？ 咁撚蠢都有嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有冇j關你撚事？"},{"pid":"2b7573987944c14a553ca9168ef36c7aec434584","tid":284690,"uid":8103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T16:41:22.000Z","msg":"條魚好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8721b90171a31572b7a0cd21807a197fc53df2","tid":284690,"uid":23535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T18:16:10.000Z","msg":"冇養開魚<br />\nD 留言好能好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12e66e5e6d4837656c22a59baa0e4cad96fa1d9","tid":284690,"uid":442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T18:27:25.000Z","msg":"幅相好似生化危機咁"},{"pid":"5c2aca50fa568286e4a459c301a0a0bf036e73ed","tid":284690,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T18:35:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗只係因為壞左過濾令水質變差同埋含氧量低<br />\n買返個上水泵換落去就得<br />\n個水泵有寫牌子型號流量<br />\n影張相去跟住買返就得<br />\n買嗰陣唔需要同店員有任何交流<br />\n一手交錢一手交貨<br />\n當你一問<br />\n佢地就知道你唔識<br />\n會水你買啲唔需要嘅野<br />\n你當自己係水族師咁行入去行返出黎就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後換7成水<br />\n加水慢慢加<br />\n白綿污糟就換<br />\n得閒就洗埋濾材<br />\n沖沖水就得<br />\n咁基本上都無乜問題<br />\n呢啲魚粗生到爆<br />\n原本係食用魚黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n長遠黎講加個氣泵好啲<br />\n雖然唔加都得<br />\n但有總好過冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以去金魚街卡奇買勁靜G30<br />\n$150左右，最抵用<br />\n夠勁夠靜夠平夠耐用<br />\n<br />\n上面好多話咩新水唔可以即刻落缸<br />\n又話咩自來水有氯氣<br />\n其實唔撚驚<br />\n驚就買支去氯劑就得<br />\n而正路黎講<br />\n如果唔係住村屋/唐樓/大廈低層或者個別會自己再加氯嘅屋苑<br />\n基本上自來水直車入缸都無問題<br />\n我就是成功的例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多人都未試過就聽人講唔可以咁做<br />\n怯你就輸一世！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放膽試一次就明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span 